snippet.title: Mario vs. Donkey Kong — A Heist of Mini Proportions — Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
When all the Mini-Marios sell out, Donkey Kong takes matters into his own hands! Track them down in the Mario vs. Donkey Kong game, available February 16, 2024, only on the Nintendo Switch system. Pre-orders are available now on Nintendo eShop.

https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/mario-vs-donkey-kong-switch/

#MariovsDonkeyKong #NintendoSwitch
